n off-screen production roles.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"his own television production company\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"post\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"departure\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"The One Show\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"screen\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"off-screen production roles\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, his plans took a relentless twist following an idea pitched by a TV commissioner.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his plans\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"a relentless twist\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"an idea\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"a TV commissioner\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amidst collating ideas for his new project, a disconcerting call from his dad broke the news of the unfortunate incident involving his mother and their immediate need for hospitalisation.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"collating ideas\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"his new project\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"a disconcerting call\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"his dad\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"the unfortunate incident\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"his mother\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"their immediate need\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"hospitalisation\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without hesitation, the host recounted how he rapidly mobilised his family and livestock, making an urgent beeline back to their northern homestead.