rom\": 1361, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We put all the animals in the trailer and headed up north.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the animals\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the trailer\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just started to do these changes because we needed to change the sheep that we had.\\\"\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these changes\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1509}, {\"ngram\": \"the sheep\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While discussing his farmhouse disorder with television commissioners for new idea suggestions, one of them proposed bringing Matt's family farm mayhem to television viewers.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his farmhouse disorder\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"television commissioners\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"new idea suggestions\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt's family farm mayhem\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"television viewers\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Initial hesitation was the response from the presenter who had not previously involved his family on-screen, but they warmed to the idea once he assured them he would be in charge of the production process.\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Initial hesitation\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"the response\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"the presenter\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"screen\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"th